/*
ABOUT
This site skin uses code based off ElectricAlice's iPad fix for their Tide skin. 
This will work regardless of if you are using the light or dark version of Stardust.
Note that these code comments will vanish when you click 'submit' to make the site skin, so make sure you can refrence this webpage if needed.
*/

/*
IMPORTANT
This skin is a work in progress. I am working on streamlining and improving it. I have not tested it with other types of tablets.
*/

/*
TO USE
(this will be on my Ao3 post but just incase.)
Copy all of this into the Ao3 CSS box for your new skin. Call it something like 'Stardust Ipad fix' for convenience sake. 
If you use Ao3 mainly or only on mobile or iPad DO NOT click use but still submit this skin.
You need to make the mobile fix skin and then do some fiddling with parent skins and media settings in the advanced skin making settings. 
Don't worry I will explain this in the mobile skin code comments.
*/

/*
STARDUST iPad fix.
*/

#workskin {
  margin: auto;
}

#workskin,
.system .userstuff,
.collection blockquote.userstuff {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 45em;
}

div#inner {
  width: 100%;
}
/*
This makes the filter bar wider so it fits on the screen correctly.
*/

.filters dl,
.filters dt {
  width: 100%;
}

/*
This makes the checkboxes bigger because I found them hard to click on ipad.
*/


.filters [type=radio] + .indicator:before,
.filters [type=radio]:checked + .indicator:before,
.filters [type=checkbox] + .indicator:before,
.filters .exclude [type=checkbox] + .indicator:before,
.filters [type=checkbox]:checked + .indicator:before,
.filters .exclude [type=checkbox]:checked + .indicator:before,
input[type=checkbox],
input[type=radio],
input[type=checkbox]:checked,
input[type=radio]:checked,
.actions input[type=checkbox]:checked,
label.action input[type=checkbox]:checked,
input[type=checkbox]:hover,
.actions input[type=checkbox]:hover {
  width: 1em;
  height: 1em;
}
/*
I think this makes text boxes display correclty? I can't recall if this worked so may remove it.
*/

fieldset {
  width: 100%;
}
